org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.grouping.tuples

Class LabelGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple
      • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple5<String,String,List<String>,List<AggregateFunction>,List<PropertyValue>>
        • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.grouping.tuples.LabelGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class LabelGroup
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple5<String,String,List<String>,List<AggregateFunction>,List<PropertyValue>>
    Stores grouping keys and aggregates for a specific label. 
     f0: grouping label
 f1: group label
 f2: property keys
 f3: aggregate functions
 f4: aggregate values
    See Also:
